Rockland Trust | .Net Developer | Plymouth, MA | Temporary | Onsite

https://rocklandtrust.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?...

Calling all IT professionals who have .Net, C# and SQL Server experience. We're looking for a Temporary Developer who can build an in-house application system to track performance appraisals. If you've utilized open source frameworks like Bootstrap or jQuery, this could be the project for you!
